cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.DS 

The paper deals with the problem of online recommendation, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of latent factor analysis and modeling of non-linear interactions between features suggests that the paper may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) subcategories. The focus on online recommendation and lightweight updates suggests that the paper may also belong to the subcategories of social and information networks (cs.SI) and data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
